       11,
       "threading.Thread.join.__qualname__.__len__() == 11 — the string 'Thread.join' has exactly 11 characters: T-h-r-e-a-d-.-j-o-i-n; str.__len__() returns 11; new to extra158"]
    - [thread_start_qualname_len_eq_12,
